The original function call is :
(planeRANSAC filename confidence percentage eps) and returns (numberOfNeighbors plane)

Example: 
(planeRANSAC "Point_Cloud_1_No_Road_Reduced.xyz" 0.99 0.88 0.0005)
and the output comes in the form of: 
(5 (-14.551006516458882 -49.71795779666572 205.04443230792964 -23.330911325035174))
